Theme setting

.libPaths("~/R/x86_64-pc-linux-gnu-library/4.1")
r2resize::add.resizer(
  theme.color = "blue",
  position = "top",
  font.size = "green",
  font.color = "blue",
  tables = TRUE,
  images = TRUE,
  line.width = 250
  )
